        "content": "<p>Justin Searls from <a href=\"https://justin.searls.co/casts/\">Breaking Change</a> joins the show to discuss Apple's Intelligence blunder, the end of the good times in the tech industry, and <a href=\"https://posseparty.com\">POSSE Party</a>, his in-progress product that lets \"any dummy with a website enjoy a life of algorithm-free luxury.\" <span aria-label=\"link\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f517\" role=\"img\" title=\"link\">:link:</span> <a href=\"https://changelog.am/85\">https://changelog.am/85</a></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Ch</th>\n<th>Start</th>\n<th>Title</th>\n<th>Runs</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>01</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/85#t=0\">00:00</a></td>\n<td>Let's talk!</td>\n<td>00:38</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>02</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/85#t=38\">00:38</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://retool.com/changelog\">Sponsor: Retool</a></td>\n<td>03:01</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>03</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/85#t=219\">03:39</a></td>\n<td>Monologues &amp; Friends</td>\n<td>07:20</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>04</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/85#t=659\">10:59</a></td>\n<td>Rotten Cupertino</td>\n<td>05:35</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>05</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/85#t=994\">16:34</a></td>\n<td>Lost credibility</td>\n<td>05:56</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>06</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/85#t=1351\">22:31</a></td>\n<td>No more real demos</td>\n<td>03:33</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>07</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/85#t=1564\">26:04</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.augmentcode.com\">Sponsor: Augment Code</a></td>\n<td>03:07</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>08</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/85#t=1750\">29:10</a></td>\n<td>What went wrong?</td>\n<td>03:12</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>09</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/85#t=1942\">32:22</a></td>\n<td>A Siri theory</td>\n<td>04:18</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/85#t=2199\">36:39</a></td>\n